{"tid":589413,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日宵夜] 自製超麻煩多工序日式薯仔沙律","createTime":"2018-03-12T00:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T09:18:30.000Z","uid":43041,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"092d595eea9ea02141abe0fdc23837c6cc2cd942","tid":589413,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"今次個薯仔沙律步驟繁複<br />\n如果唔係條仔鍾意食真係未必會整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企又無壓薯仔個件野<br />\n手都斷啊屌拿星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/075601_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F075601_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=20beebca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新手唔識批皮，上網搵到方法<br />\n洗完薯仔後係中間輕輕圍住薯仔一圈介一刀<br />\n然後先拎去煮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2aab0f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮薯仔期間將青瓜切片，落鹽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080113_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c6bdd3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣可以令青瓜既水份流出，好似會爽口d，放10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080209_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080209_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8896f740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薯仔煮熟之後可以剝皮，因為有刀痕所以應該超容易就成塊起到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ecf75b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最麻煩既工序就係依度<br />\n無壓薯工具就用叉壓成蓉啦<br />\n頂硬上，手都斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082320_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c7b8724f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個青瓜已經淋曬<br />\n用廚紙包好，然後用手搾汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/080528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F080528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f789aedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搾完出黎既青瓜皺曬皮<br />\n拎出黎放埋一邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cbd1d91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烚全熟蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081306_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081306_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3d205c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切碎，加入蛋黃醬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af7c74ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落黑椒、鹽同小小basil，撈勻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081549_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081549_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45c110f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同薯蓉搞埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=16085d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入青瓜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081707_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1209117d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小蟹柳～～ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/081727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F081727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8b0b1ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好食還好食，不過好撚多工夫，人都癲"},{"pid":"a73d52846baac1358854282e7c8ccc8608960420","tid":589413,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"用罐頭蟹肉好d"},{"pid":"c2d1424bbab6d5199e8fc654ed0408b5841f11b8","tid":589413,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a73d52846baac1358854282e7c8ccc8608960420","tid":589413,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"用罐頭蟹肉好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:05:57.